description: [DarkGate](https://attack.mitre.org/software/S1111) tries to elevate privileges to SYSTEM using PsExec to locally execute as a service, such as cmd /c c:\temp\PsExec.exe -accepteula -j -d -s [Target Binary].(Citation: Trellix Darkgate 2023)
